Package: syrinx
Title: Data Harmonization Tools for Internal Use
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Joe", "Corra", , "corra.joseph@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A set of functions to harmonize and standardize datasets for
    greenhouse gas emissions inventories. Includes data dictionary validation,
    LLM-assisted value correction, unit conversion to canonical units, and
    metadata labeling.
